            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>Visualization</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>: Improved visual aesthetics by changing colors and sorting in descending order by Sales. Changed axis labes to custom currency.</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>Analysis</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>: This chart highlights the sales teams that exceeded their goal as well as those who did not meet their goals. These are the Sales by team for 2019. The next sheet includes the 2020 chart for Sales by Sales Team.</run>
