            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>Analysis</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>: This dual axis line chart show that Sales and Profit rise and fall accordingly. The chart shows an upward trend from 2018-2020 and from 2019-2020. However,  when filtered down to 2020, over $100K decrease in Sales and Profit is shown. The trend line helps to visualize the increase or decrease in both measures.</run>
