            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>Analysis</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial'>: This bar chart provides an overall view at profit by category. Sorted in descending order, it is easy to see that Tech Accessories rank the highest and Executive Office ranks the lowest in terms of profit for all years. Filters allow user to compare categories within the selected Region and Year. Reference line is added to show how each category compares to the average. </run>
