            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Visualization</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>: Changed circle shape and size to make values more visible. </run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>Analysis</run>
            <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Arial' fontsize='10'>: Visualizing the sales to profit ratio in its respective year shows each order is profitable (&gt;0) and the trend line shows what should be expected, an upward trend, that as sales increases profit increases. The comparison between 2018, 2019, and 2020 show that the sales to profit ratio in 2019 was slightly less than 2018 and 2020.</run>
