        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11618' id='6' story-point-id='1' type-v2='text' w='56102' x='17520' y='41183'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>The company has been profitable from 2018 to 2020, but progress within recent years has a constant and slightly negative trend. Sales of 2018 began in Quarter 2, therefore total sales and profit are expected to be lower than 2019 and 2020. Select different years to see that profit in 2019 increased by over $30,000, but profit in 2020 decreased by over $100,000. We should look for areas to improve for next year.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11722' hidden='true' id='7' story-point-id='2' type-v2='text' w='36220' x='28543' y='51763'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Tech categories such as Video Games, Phones, and Tech Accesories were highly profitable each year. A deeper look, by year, into Misc. Gaming Furniture show a jump in profit between 2018 to 2020. Category profit by year shows potential for growth and areas of concern. Click on each year to see how category profit fluctuated.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='8402' hidden='true' id='8' story-point-id='5' type-v2='text' w='36319' x='57579' y='49066'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontsize='10'>With sales and profit average as a reference, see the highest and lowest ranking categories. Hover over any data point to see total Profit and Sales.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='12033' hidden='true' id='9' story-point-id='3' type-v2='text' w='43209' x='19488' y='33402'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>All customers from 2018 returned, however this chart highlights those with decreased order counts. Hover over light blue (2020) to see the difference from 2019. While the difference ranges from -1 to -15 , considering that a total of 21 of 50 customers had drops in order counts provides insight into the the constant or negative sales trend.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='9959' hidden='true' id='10' story-point-id='6' type-v2='text' w='40551' x='28248' y='34025'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#333333' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>Top sales team exceeded their annual sales goal by almost $200K. A majority of sales teams either met or exceeded their goal, but scroll to the bottom portion of this chart to see the few teams that were shy of their goal. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='9025' hidden='true' id='11' story-point-id='7' type-v2='text' w='32382' x='18504' y='29357'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>A visual comparison between profit by Sales Channels indicate the $1M differences of IQRs. Ranking highest with IQR at $4 - $5M is In-Store and the lowest is Wholesale at above $1M in profit.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='7261' hidden='true' id='12' story-point-id='8' type-v2='text' w='37402' x='27854' y='40560'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>The West Region is significantly more profitable than the Northeast. Click to see the profit by region for each year and the same ranking holds true. </run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='11411' hidden='true' id='13' story-point-id='9' type-v2='text' w='45768' x='21063' y='17427'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='10'>While the previous chart showed the high profitability of the West Region, this map shows that California brings in significant sales. Most of the continental US are consumers of company products, but there is room for growth into Wyoming, W.Virginia, Maine, and Vermont. Profit by the various fields in this analysis bring key insights into high performers and areas with potential.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='13900' hidden='true' id='14' story-point-id='10' type-v2='text' w='62795' x='22539' y='40456'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>Key Insights Recap</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>1. Constant and slightly negative 2020 Time Series trend show that Sales can improve.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>2. Customers with decreased order counts should be looked into.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>3. Promote bestselling categories to make up for decreased sales.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>4. Sales team performance can be improved using strategies from goal-exceeding teams.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>5. Sales channel visualization shows that in-store sales perform best.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#1b1b1b' fontname='Tableau Light' fontsize='9'>6. The West Region earns the highest profit, mainly due to California sales. There is room for growth within each state as well as building customer relations with more continental US states.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{89D09E93-753E-46FD-9EA5-938A3D54F1C8}' />
    </dashboard>
